---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service - Pressly">
	<div class="relative min-h-screen bg-[#F8FAFC] selection:bg-primary/20 selection:text-primary pb-32">
		<!-- Minimalist Hero -->
		<div class="relative pt-32 pb-24 overflow-hidden flex flex-col items-center text-center px-6">
			<!-- Subtle mesh background -->
			<div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none z-0 flex items-center justify-center">
				<div class="w-[800px] h-[800px] bg-gradient-to-tl from-slate-200/50 via-primary/5 to-slate-100/50 rounded-full blur-[100px] opacity-70"></div>
			</div>
			
			<div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<span class="inline-block py-1 px-3 rounded-full bg-white border border-slate-200 text-xs font-bold tracking-widest text-slate-500 uppercase mb-6 animate-fade-in-up">Legal</span>
				<h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-display font-extrabold text-slate-900 tracking-tight mb-6 animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.1s;">
					Rules of the road,<br/>
					<span class="text-slate-900">simplified.</span>
				</h1>
				<p class="text-xl text-slate-500 font-medium animate-fade-in-up" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
					Clear terms for a seamless laundry experience.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>

		<!-- Main Document Container -->
		<div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
			<div class="bg-white rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-16 lg:p-20 shadow-[0_20px_60px_-15px_rgba(0,0,0,0.05)] border border-slate-100/50 animate-fade-in-up mb-20" style="animation-delay: 0.3s;">
				
				<div class="flex items-center justify-between pb-8 border-b border-slate-100 mb-12">
					<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest">Effective Date</p>
					<p class="text-sm font-medium text-slate-900 bg-slate-100 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">June 2026</p>
				</div>

				<div class="space-y-16 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-sans">
					
					<!-- Section 1 -->
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">1. Welcome to Pressly</h2>
						<p class="mb-4">
							By downloading, accessing, or using the Pressly application and website, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to all of the terms and conditions, you must not use our services.
						</p>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 2 -->
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">2. Our Services</h2>
						<p class="mb-6">
							Pressly operates as a technology platform connecting users seeking laundry and ironing services with independent local vendors. 
						</p>
						
						<div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-100 mt-8">
							<h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-4 text-xl">What we do:</h3>
							<ul class="space-y-4">
								<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
									<span>Facilitate the booking and scheduling of services.</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
									<span>Process payments securely on behalf of the vendors.</span>
								</li>
								<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
									<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="text-green-500 shrink-0 mt-0.5"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
									<span>Provide customer support and mediation in case of disputes.</span>
								</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 3 -->
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">3. User Responsibilities</h2>
						<p class="mb-4">
							As a user of Pressly, you agree to:
						</p>
						<ul class="space-y-4 mt-6">
							<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="mt-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
									<span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-600">1</span>
								</div>
								<span>Provide accurate contact and address information for pickups.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="mt-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
									<span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-600">2</span>
								</div>
								<span>Ensure clothes handed over do not contain hazardous materials or valuables left in pockets.</span>
							</li>
							<li class="flex items-start gap-4">
								<div class="mt-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-200 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
									<span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-600">3</span>
								</div>
								<span>Maintain the confidentiality of your account credentials.</span>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</section>

					<!-- Section 4 -->
					<section>
						<h2 class="text-3xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mb-6 tracking-tight">4. Liability & Limitations</h2>
						<p>
							While we thoroughly vet our vendors, Pressly acts as an intermediary platform. We hold liability for platform uptime and payment processing. Liability for damaged or lost clothing is mediated by Pressly but ultimately lies within the specific vendor's service agreement, up to a maximum defined compensation limit outlined in our app.
						</p>
					</section>
					
					<!-- Section 5 -->
					<section class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 p-8 md:p-10 rounded-3xl mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-start sm:items-center justify-between gap-6">
						<div>
							<h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2 tracking-tight">Need clarification?</h2>
							<p class="text-slate-500">
								Our support team is available 24/7.
							</p>
						</div>
						<a href="mailto:support@pressly.app" class="inline-flex shrink-0 items-center gap-2 bg-slate-900 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded-xl font-bold hover:bg-slate-800 transition-colors">
							Contact Support
							<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14"/><path d="m12 5 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
						</a>
					</section>

				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
